data.description: Make yourself welcome to this beautiful two-story single-family home nestled in the quiet, tranquil neighborhood of Sweetwater Bend.  Offering plenty of natural light throughout the house, you will find three bedrooms with a full hallway bathroom accompanied by a primary suite, including a large walk-in closet, spacious full bathroom with dual vanity, jetted tub, and walk-in shower, laminate flooring throughout the house and updated amenities, which include black stainless-steel appliances in the kitchen.  Other updated improvements include newer washer and dryer in the main floor laundry room, forced-air furnace, central air, and a newer roof.  There is also plenty of room to grow with an unfinished walk-out basement. So, whether you are inside, comforted by the warmth of the gas fireplace, or outside lounging on the spacious deck overlooking the fenced in yard and basketball court, come make this your next home!
